I stand before this court today to wholeheartedly plead guilty to the offense of accepting bribes. I fully acknowledge my involvement in the act of accepting a total of 4000 pounds in exchange for not publishing an article exposing a company's false emission claims. I understand the seriousness of my actions and take full responsibility for the consequences they have brought upon me.

