Allowing the greenwashing of the company to continue for a short period of time was a direct consequence of my actions. However, I want to highlight that my role in this offense was limited. It is important to note that the true emission numbers were ultimately exposed by someone else just 5 weeks later, rendering my actions ultimately ineffective. Nevertheless, I deeply regret my part in perpetuating the deception and the negative impact it may have had.

I am aware of the harm caused by allowing the company's greenwashing to continue, and I accept the consequences that come with it. I stand before you today with a firm commitment to making amends and ensuring that such actions will never be repeated. I fully understand the gravity of my offense and the need for accountability.

By presenting this guilty plea, I hope to demonstrate to the court the level of ownership I have taken for my wrongdoing. Recognizing the importance of accountability, I am providing the court with my full cooperation as an active participant in the legal process.

Thank you for allowing me to address the court. I appreciate your consideration of the circumstances surrounding my involvement and request your leniency in light of my guilty plea.

Sincerely,
Jack Palmer

